(7231, 'en', 'LayerSlider', '52d096db2d41c73e647fc7b4afe9f4fb', 'Fades the layer. You can use values between 1 and 0 to set the layer fully opaque or transparent respectively. For example, the value 0.5 will make the layer semi-transparent.', NULL, 'LINE', NULL, 0, '', 'e9a8f7b4c8ca6334949a519c089ba2bf'),
